Package com.deco2800.game.memento

Class Player

java.lang.Object
com.deco2800.game.memento.Player
public class Player
extends java.lang.Object
Originator which is used to store player state internally. Originator has a method which will create a memento object to store its internal state and this memento object is then added to a history list of all memento objects created in the past. It is able to restore itself to a past originator if needed to restore a player state
